Class IComboBoxModel<T extends SonarObject>

java.lang.Object
javax.swing.AbstractListModel<T>
us.mn.state.dot.tms.client.widget.IComboBoxModel<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, ComboBoxModel<T>, ListModel<T>
public class IComboBoxModel<T extends SonarObject> extends AbstractListModel<T> implements ComboBoxModel<T>
IComboBoxModel is a ComboBoxModel which can be used as a wrapper for a ProxyListModel. It is useful for making multiple JComboBoxes which have the same underlying ListModel, but have a different "selection".
Author:
Douglas Lau
